{
  "stem": "935.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that was only few days before the invasion of Holland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because Belgium got-- a matter of fact, when I got to, to Holland, I missed the Stormtroopers by two days.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Or, rather, they missed me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So then I was in Holland and got my apartment back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And on May 10, 1940, the invasion of Holland took place-- lasted five days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lived in a very pretty residential square.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember, on the corner of that, there was a military [? kasern. ?] And I'd never seen anybody in there before.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And just a couple of days before the invasion, I saw some soldiers there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were walking around with a cigarette in their mouths and with open things, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't-- no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have to realize Holland didn't have a war for hundred years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And also, anti-Semitism has never existed in Holland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the, the Dutch Jews, shoemakers, and bankers, and, and little tailors, or selling eel on the street, and industrialists.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So is, you know, there is both.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When the invasion took place, it was very weird.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It is like somebody shows you a lot of slides.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they're faulty-- and very rapidly, very rapidly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The radio would say, we don't have anything to worry about and the bombs already dropped.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everything is under control.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And people are running back and forth and into each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then, then we heard the queen had fled.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, it was total commotion, total-- nobody knew what to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They didn't have an army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they thought that if they open all the dams, the Germans can't march in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, in a very, very peculiar, sinister way, they were right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because they didn't march.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
